{"tid":783361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美帝國防部分析支那軍力發展","createTime":"2018-08-17T12:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T13:09:48.000Z","uid":98659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2a5dc27cb3df721398b8cf802d2071583e34e480","tid":783361,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:59:28.000Z","msg":"進行了史上最大規模的組織重整工作，包括解編5個集團軍與指揮體系的扁平化<br />\n<br />\n持續強化長程打擊火力，但戰術機隊僅有少量的（a small number）空射導引武器（火箭大法好）<br />\n<br />\n 預警機隊與各式防空武器建立沿海300哩內的防空網<br />\n<br />\n利用OTH雷達與衛星建立反艦彈道飛彈的耳目 <br />\n<br />\n 空射長劍巡弋飛彈加入了光電導引<br />\n<br />\n中國在五代機的雷達與引擎的發展仍有困難（having difficulty with the engines and radars）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/military.flak/?fref=tag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmilitary.flak%2F%3Ffref%3Dtag&d=gymw88FKLZleXhCH8leI0r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=3c6d9db4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/military.flak/?fref=tag</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://media.defense.gov/2018/Aug/16/2001955282/-1/-1/1/2018-CHINA-MILITARY-POWER-REPORT.PDF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.defense.gov%2F2018%2FAug%2F16%2F2001955282%2F-1%2F-1%2F1%2F2018-CHINA-MILITARY-POWER-REPORT.PDF&d=gymw88FKLZleXhCH8leI0r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a2dee116\" target=\"_blank\">https://media.defense.gov/2018/Aug/16/2001955282/-1/-1/1/2018-CHINA-MILITARY-POWER-REPORT.PDF</a>"},{"pid":"4872f8e602d8f37996ad0568de6ef87508313e6b","tid":783361,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"快Ｄ係台灣開個新美軍基地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.g